    <title>Session 27: Examples of universal constructions, Part 13</title>
    <p>
       The end of the session is in sight, but simultaneously seems so
       far away.  I still feel like I'm uncertain about whether or not
       my depection of the equalizer in <xref ref="session27-p10">Exercise 8</xref> 
